cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation accuracy. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as these fields are closely related to natural language processing and translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with the accuracy of retrieving information through translation. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as neural networks are often used in machine translation.
